title: Check Out This Video Of Kareena Kapoor Receiving A Filmfare Award From Karisma Kapoor
text:
Sukriti Gumber Mar . 20 . 2017 Kareena Kapoor 
Kareena Kapoor Khan has been ruling the industry ever since she made her debut with Refugee , back in 2000. She has been around for almost 17 years – and been on numero uno position no less! Ah well, she is Bebo after all! 
One of the best performances of Kareena’s career was in Chameli , that came quite early on in her career. She even won a Filmfare Award for her performance in the film, given to her by none other than her sister, Karisma Kapoor . Check out this video: 
How lovely do these ladies look (as always)?!
